text: Jarosław Lato (born 17 June 1977 in Świdnica) is a retired Polish footballer (winger). He is not related to Grzegorz Lato. ==Career== ===Club=== Lato has also played for Stal Świdnica, Lechia Dzierżoniów, Śląsk Wrocław, RKS Radomsko, Widzew Łódź, Dyskobolia Grodzisk, Polonia Warsaw and Jagiellonia Białystok. He was released from Jagiellonia Białystok on 24 June 2011.Jagiellonia pożegnała się z Jarosławem Latą 24.06.2011, onet.pl ==Successes== * 1x Polish Cup Winner (2006/07) with Dyskobolia Grodzisk Wielkopolski. * 2x Ekstraklasa Cup Winner (2007), (2008) with Dyskobolia Grodzisk Wielkopolski. * 1x Polish Cup Winner (2010) with Jagiellonia Białystok. * 1x Polish SuperCup Winner (2010) with Jagiellonia Białystok. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:People from Świdnica Category:Polish footballers Category:Dyskobolia Grodzisk Wielkopolski players Category:Polonia Warsaw players Category:Śląsk Wrocław players Category:Widzew Łódź players Category:RKS Radomsko players Category:Jagiellonia Białystok players Category:Association football midfielders Category:Sportspeople from Lower Silesian Voivodeship
